import { Box, Container, Paper, TextField } from "@mui/material";
import React from "react";

function SchoolForm(props) {
  return (
    <>
      <Container maxWidth="sm">
        <Paper variant="outlined">
          <Box mt={3}>
            <TextField
              id="outlined-basic"
              label="No. Of Students"
              variant="outlined"
              fullWidth
              required
            />
          </Box>
          <Box mt={3}>
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              id="outlined-basic"
              variant="outlined"
              label="Total Classes"
              required
              size="medium"
            ></TextField>
          </Box>
          <Box mt={3}>
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              id="outlined-basic"
              variant="outlined"
              label="Expense "
              required
              size="medium"
            ></TextField>
          </Box>
          <Box mt={3}>
            <TextField
              fullWidth
              id="outlined-basic"
              variant="outlined"
              label="Revenue"
              required
              size="medium"
            ></TextField>
          </Box>
        </Paper>
      </Container>
    </>
  );
}

export default SchoolForm;
